<li>
  <h3><a name="f1"></a>Adding Smacks</h3>
  <ol start="1" type="1">
    <li>Sign in to your Campusmack account.</li>
    <li>Using the side navigation bar, hover over the conference of the team you wish to Smack. Click on the
      College you want to Smack on the list that pops up, this will take you to that College’s main landing page.
    </li>
    <li>Click on the <%= image_tag('about/add_smack.jpg') %>  button at the top right hand corner of the page.</li>
    <li>Click the box to the right of the “Post type:” label corresponding to the type of post you’d like to
      upload:  <%= image_tag('about/post_type.jpg') %></li>
    <li>Type in a Title for the post.</li>
    <li>For Video posts, just paste in a Youtube URL in the “URL” field. For Photo posts, click the “Browse”
      button and upload a photo. For News articles, just paste in the URL of the article you want to share. You
      can add either a Photo or Video to a News article by clicking the “Add Photo” or “Add Video” link beneath
      the “Article URL:” box.
    </li>
    <li>Type in a summary of the content you plan to upload in the "Summary:" box.</li>
    <li>Click the <%= image_tag('about/submit.jpg') %> button and the information will be posted to the College
      you selected.
    </li>
  </ol>
</li>
<li>
